br />\n當然你一開始係打算長渣, 咁祝你好運<br />\n恆指殺到上二萬八的話, 你仲有機會<br />\n<br />\n祝你好運"},{"pid":"a383122c42bf57d77864c963cb57b474168c1178","tid":163740,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/20/161330_b23272173b67345ae51ab7880515ca16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F20%2F161330_b23272173b67345ae51ab7880515ca16.jpg&h=490ff5c0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n6千定5萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nX2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為個價位有好多盤, 5000, 3000, 咁如果一次入晒5萬股, 其實係唔止一個trade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得似假膠，但又冇人問，點知俾人串第一次買股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f55ac3dd50b58e95f8eb4d8a041c701067797eb","tid":163740,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連續賣帳面蝕 25粒+<br />\n<br />\n樓主, 止蝕喇, 有賭未為輸<br />\n唔好為啖氣, 而坐落去<br />\n我唔敢講佢升唔番上去<br />\n但如果你一開始係打算短炒, 你就應該止蝕<br />\n當然你一開始係打算長渣, 咁祝你好運<br />\n恆指殺到上二萬八的話, 你仲有機會<br />\n<br />\n祝你好運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n廿粒野姐,仲未有技術調整張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777857edf3f8842b163a73798e43260cdad709ae","tid":163740,"uid":76845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"輸少當贏"},{"pid":"51b41ec5d0dc2dcfc4499a123492b48f2917a32a","tid":163740,"uid":44165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T09:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連續賣帳面蝕 25粒+<br />\n<br />\n樓主, 止蝕喇, 有賭未為輸<br />\n唔好為啖氣, 而坐落去<br />\n我唔敢講佢升唔番上去<br />\n但如果你一開始係打算短炒, 你就應該止蝕<br />\n當然你一開始係打算長渣, 咁祝你好運<b